                           <p>Titles and inital words in larger square characters.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Marginal notes in Oriental cursive script, and also enumerations of sections added in an Italian cursive script. Parts of the notes have been folded inwards, e.g. folio 8-10, 20, 147, 181.</p>
                           
                           
                           
